<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dissociative_drug">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dissociative_drug</a></p>
<p>except Larry isn't a <em>drug</em>, it's a two-person llama costume wearing galoshes.</p>
<p>They were using Larry for recreational purposes, to achieve an effect similar to that caused by dissociative drugs. It was psychic-dissociative recreation: recreation that involved having their psyches dissociate.</p>

